# Latex template
Simple Latex template with CI/CD.

Requirements:
* pdflatex (for pdf output)
* make4ht (for html output)
* latexmk

Usage:
* Just run
    $ make
* Cleanup with
    $ make clean

To use in your project just:
* Clone
    $ git clone git@github.com:laudominik/latex-project-template.git example
    $ cd example
* Reinitialize repo
    $ rm -Rf .git
    $ git init

Or just use the provided script:
    $ curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/laudominik/latex-project-template/refs/heads/main/scripts/create_project.sh | bash -s example
